{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Albert Rosa-- A-L-B-E-R-T, R-O-S-A.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Abraham Rosa.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "January the 25th, 1925.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 70 years now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Greece, Salonika.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war-- I-- I come from a religious family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- my father had a hardware store-- which we was middle class people-- probably a little bit upper middle class.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I was a young teenager going to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very much involved in sports.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was-- my brother was one of the big shots in the Hakoah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's an Jewish organization for sports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- he-- he took me when I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not allowed to be there that young, but he sneaked me in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to box there, play soccer, ping pong, and swimming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we used to compete with different other people, especially with the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because the reason we have to learn how to box-- in case we have to defend ourselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a very nice life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- by Friday, by the night-- Shabbes-- we used to come the whole family together and to make the Kaddish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, like I-- like I said, they were Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we have very good life till the war started in 1939, in Greece, against the Italians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Italians bombed all over Greece.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Italians was losing the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they-- then they called help-- for the Germans to come over there to help them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Germans come over, a small country like Greece, they couldn't survive against Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think there was about nine months in the war against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally, they lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans occupy that-- Greece.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They occupy Salonika.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and then when the problem starts.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
